node.text: My mum makes the best chicken stew! It’s a one dish in a pot that is really easy to make! Imagine chicken with super crispy skin that is in a pot of thick flavour-bursting gravy with lots of carrots, celery, onions, potatoes and a sprinkle of black pepper, rosemary and thyme for that extra flavour! We call it the happy celebratory dish at home, cos it only makes its appearance together with wine when we have something to celebrate in the family!  Also I can’t wait to go back to my parent’s place after CB ends for my home cooked bday dinner celebration! 😀 😛  @coff_n_choc @claudio.chock @djblaqjacq

My mom Signature dish spring roll popiah absolutely delight to pair well with thai chillie sauce.👍👍👍
Fried popiah - spring roll 
Ingredients 
4 pieces tau kwa 
5 potatoes 
1 carrot
1 chicken breast 
1 packet of popiah skin 
2 clove of garlic 
4 tbsp oil
3 tbsp corn flour add hot water mixed for roll and seal. 
All ingredients Cut cubes 
Seasoning oyster sauce, pepper 
In a preheated wok, heat oil until hot and 1.fry potatoes and carrot until soft remove and set aside. 
Fried tau kwa and add 1. Potatoes and carrots in and add chicken breast stir fried them together and add oysters sauce and pepper to taste. 
Allow the filling to cool 
Spring roll wrapping, leave outside 1hour thaw before using.
Place a piece of wrapper on a clean surface,  and add ingredients in the centre toward you and fold in both corners and roll up. 
In a wok heat oil and fry until golden brown 2 to 3 minutes. 
Remove and drain. 
Serve dish with thai chilli sauce and garnish  with sliced of tomatoes and lettuce. 👍👍👍
Fb Toh Layhoon

Thanks for the awesome giveaway by Rinnai Holdings Pacific! Steamed CodFish will be one of my favourite dishes! This fish is my favourite. No matter, how expensive the fish is, my mummy will always buy it for the family. I love codfish, best steamed. Only fresh fish tastes the best. Simply yummilicious. Often a time, it is said the more fish you eat, the smartest one will be. I cannot wait to win this cookery for my mummy so that she can cook more delicious meals for the family as she deserves the best.
Even the simplest dish, it can be delicious! She always has the best thoughts for all of us, always give us the best that she can. Mother's Day is arriving real soon!
I appreciate my mom because she is a petite, hardworking, independant wife, mother and daughter who always has the best thoughts for her hubby, children and siblings.
She has been working hard to support the family. After her work, she never fails to cook hot-piping meals for the family. During her non-working days, she will go out for exercise to strengthen herself too. She always believe we need to build up our stamina and do not be a couch potato at home.
Her love for the children is beyond description. Time spent with her is precious and to treasure. During this difficult times, I cannot wait to show my love for her by blessing her with this fantastic prize. I love you mummy! My way to show her i love you! Your love is simply amazing! Thank you for everything! @jolin9087 @freanilis @lisachan922  FB: Bycl Lim

My mother makes real yummy Curry Tonkatsu which never fails to keep me salivating ✌️
Anyone can be a mother, but it takes real efforts to be a wonderful mother! Mine is the perfect example ❤ She has been the HEROINE of my life because:
[M] aster in her culinary skills
[O] utstanding [T] ender loving care for our family
[H] eart of gold
[E] ducating us in our daily lives
[R] ole model in all ways
Till date, it is heartwarming to reminisce my younger days when she will carry my school bag and hold my hands tightly as she walked me to and back from primary school ❤ Those were the mischievous side of me where I will beg and cry to eat ice-cream after school, and there comes my wonderful mother who will give in to my request despite knowing that I will ask for it the next time round - all because she just want to see a happy smile in me ❤ Now that I have grown up, I'm truly grateful and appreciative towards her upbringing and guidance ❤ 
Without her motherly advice and 
without her ultimate sacrifice,
I would have never been here today ❤
Without the support I needed from her,
I never would have succeeded thus far ❤
Without her unbounded & selfless love,
I would never become what I am today ❤
